Insulation:


=Reflectix (or another radiant barrier like EZ-Cool or Insul-shine, or an Eclipse Sunshade) 
Moveable windscreen covering for when stationary.
is only effective as a radient barrier. (do not put against walls)




Sound deadening material over entire metal frame
Polyisocyanurate (Polyiso) Foam Boards inbetween van skelaton
Glued in place with Great Stuff spray foam or 3M High Strength 90 spray adhesive
Fill in any gaps with foam spray


